## 3) License changes, updates, and termination

### 3.1 License changes
The Licensor reserves the right to change, update, or replace these licensing terms at any time.

New licensing terms may apply immediately to:
- future downloads/releases;
- future use of updated versions.

If you continue to use, copy, modify, distribute, or deploy the Project after a license update is published in this repository, you agree to the updated terms.

### 3.2 Termination
This license and the rights granted under it automatically terminate if you breach its terms.

The Licensor may also terminate this license grant for a specific user with immediate effect upon written notice.

Upon termination, you must cease all use, distribution, and Public Deployment, and remove the Project from production systems where applicable.

Sections that by their nature should survive termination (including Attribution, Warranty Disclaimer, and Limitation of Liability) survive.

### 3.3 Compliance, verification, and inquiries
If the Licensor reasonably believes you are engaged in unauthorized Commercial Use, the Licensor may contact you to request clarification. You agree to respond in good faith and provide sufficient information to confirm whether your use is Non-Commercial or Commercial.

